<div class="comment comment-published clear-block">
  <div class="comment-header clearfloat">
    <div class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="http://www.evilbunneh.com" rel="nofollow">Cliff</a> (not verified) on February 4, 2008 - 12:39pm</div>
    <div class="comment-link"><a href="/node/4524#comment-9543" class="active">#16</a></div>
