<a id="comment-10044"></a>
<div class="comment comment-published clear-block">
  <div class="comment-header clearfloat">
    <div class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="http://thepriceislol.com" rel="nofollow">Salva Veritate</a> (not verified) on February 13, 2008 - 6:47pm</div>
